u should not give permissions for knowledge base View (Global).<\/p>\n<p>Keep in mind that if the knowledge base is enabled in customers area, every visitor on the customers are will be able to read the articles.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Customers area In case you don&#8217;t need the knowledge base on the customers are there is an option to disable the knowledge base feature. To disable you need to navigate to Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;Customers and set\u00a0Use Knowledge Base to No. Staff Members If you give the staff members permissions for knowledge base View (Global) then they will [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[28],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-919","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-knowledge-base"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/919","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=919"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/919\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=919"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=919"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=919"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}